Package org.dmsextension.paperless.client

Klasse PaperlessClient.Builder

java.lang.Object
org.dmsextension.paperless.client.PaperlessClient.Builder
Umschließende Klasse:
PaperlessClient
public static class PaperlessClient.Builder extends Object
Builder class for PaperlessClient objects. Following methods must be called in order for building to be successful: - either user(String) and password(String) or interceptor(Interceptor) - either protocol(String) and host(String) and port(String) or url(String)

      public PaperlessClient.Builder interceptor(@NotNull okhttp3.Interceptor interceptor)
      Add interceptor to Builder. Interceptor should add a valid Authorization header to the api call. If interceptor is given user(String) and password(String) do not need to be called.
      Parameter:
      interceptor - Interceptor to add
